pages.title: North: The AI Platform Where Work Flows | Cohere
pages.description: North is the turnkey AI platform for workplace productivity. Build automations, chat with your data, and co-create with AI from a secure, intelligent workspace.
headings: AI for business that turns complexity into clarity
Empower your workforce with AI agents that operate in lockstep with your people, data, and tools.
This is what enterprise-ready AI looks like
Why enterprises and innovators choose Cohere

“We jointly announced a customized platform, North for Banking, to enable RBC to accelerate the development of our genAI solutions securely and efficiently and we’re pleased with our results to date. As our collaboration continues, we welcome the opportunity to use North for Banking to enable AI to unlock value across the enterprise.”

“We jointly announced a customized platform, North for Banking, to enable RBC to accelerate the development of our genAI solutions securely and efficiently and we’re pleased with our results to date. As our collaboration continues, we welcome the opportunity to use North for Banking to enable AI to unlock value across the enterprise.”
